1778588047s:920:"<h2 id="bkmrk-what-is-vatis">What is vATIS</h2>
<p id="bkmrk-vatis-is-the-softwar">vATIS is the software we use to connect and 'ATIS' online directly to the network. You may have noticed while flying that it is not just the controller themselves that is connected. An ATIS provides information about an airports conditions and NOTAM's to pilots that are flying, an example of an ATIS is bellow.</p>
